column1: #Text=What are some of your achievements as councilman in Macomb , New York ?
#Text=I am the only Democrat on the five person board .
#Text=So the entire board has to take credit of keeping tax increases below 2 % a year without going into our fund balance .
#Text=In fact our fund balance is the best of the other 31 towns and the county of St. Lawrence .
#Text=We have lowered the cost of health care along with our tax base .
#Text=Upgraded equipment , put money aside for replacement equipment , made our buildings energy efficient .
#Text=Then we started at the beginning of each meeting the Pledge of Allegiance and a short prayer to the Almighty .
#Text=Best of all we have no debt .
#Text=What are some of your achievements as chairman of the Democratic Party of St. Lawrence County ?
#Text=This was a strong Republican county when I first became chair .
#Text=I was able to turn the county around to Democrat , but now it has fallen back to Republican .
#Text=I started the first resource guide that allowed us to raise funds , obtained a house for the first time ever headquarters .
#Text=won her first Senate seat with just 10 counties out of 62 in New York .
#Text=We were one of those 10 counties when I was chair .
#Text=I served as chair and was called back after several years to be chair again .
#Text=I left the party in both a happy , strong and good financial condition .
#Text=According to WWNY-TV , you previously ran for president in 1992 .
#Text=What was the nature of that run and what did you learn from it ?
#Text=I am impressed that you did some investigative work .
#Text=You should go far in this field .
#Text=The country was just starting to feel the impact of a slowdown .
#Text=I wanted to speak out as to what I saw and speak to the issues of the day .
#Text=I learned that it was a closed shop then and has gotten worse both in ability to be recognized and the economic situation .
#Text=and all free trade policies are detrimental to our economical health , jobs , income and general well being of the country .
#Text=When NAFTA was first proposed I was chair and spoke out against it and was given heat for it .
#Text=But oh well I swim upstream anyway .
#Text=Did you run in any presidential primaries in 1992 ?
#Text=I ran in six states total and did the best [ in ] Louisiana .
#Text=What do you like about the party and have you ever considered joining a non-establishment party ?
#Text=No I will not join any other party .
#Text=I like the freedom of being a Democrat .
#Text=This freedom is not found in other parties .
